WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
[Dramatic cinematic background music begins]

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:12.000
[Stunning panoramic view of Santorini island, Greece]

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:19.500
[Parkour athlete focusing intensely, preparing for the run]

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:27.000
[He performs a spectacular backflip on the rooftop]

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
[Slow-motion camera angle captures the perfect landing]

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
[Rapid sound of footsteps echoing along the narrow stairs]

00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:55.000
[A daring leap across the precarious gap between two white buildings]

01:00:00.000 --> 01:00:05.000
[Bystanders clapping and cheering in admiration]

01:10:00.000 --> 01:10:15.000
[The music tempo increases, matching the relentless pace]

01:20:00.000 --> 01:20:25.000
[A series of masterful, back-to-back somersaults and acrobatics]

01:40:00.000 --> 01:40:45.000
[A romantic sunset begins to fall over the Aegean Sea]

02:00:00.000 --> 02:00:05.000
[The athlete stands on the cliff edge, gazing out at the horizon]

02:15:00.000 --> 02:15:10.000
[The sound of ocean wind whispering, blending with dramatic music]

03:00:00.000 --> 03:00:05.000
[Ending: The ultimate showcase of the Art of Motion and freerunning]

03:20:00.000 --> 03:25:00.000
[Music slowly fades out to an end]
